{"tid":1697932,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"好重要！12/11係呢場運動既第五個月！！！","createTime":"2019-11-07T07:20:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T19:00:03.000Z","uid":304230,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"eb02117448935f8960ffbba6842945f94fd5af5e","tid":1697932,"uid":304230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:20:52.000Z","msg":"呢五個月黎我相信大家都有好大轉變！<br />\n有人放棄左自己假期！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甚至有人放棄左前途！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去守護住我地既屋企！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地決定<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">狠狠地懲罰你地！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望可以同大家繼續一齊行落去！<br />\n一齊堅持落去！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以12/11 我地決定當日係唔會做生意！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無錯 係唔會賣飲品！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係我地係一蚊都唔會收！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為我地會準備612杯「六月飛雪」！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n派發比一齊行左咁耐既同路人！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n點先叫同路人？<br />\n<br />\n我地會講一句 只要你接到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 / 反抗！<br />\n五大訴求 / 缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地就會派一杯！就係咁簡單！<br />\n你地千奇唔好怕醜！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為派唔哂我係唔會收工架！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲有記住11/11都要黎支持！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唇茶 捐錢第二彈 「立場」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1660778\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1660778</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n暫定指定飲品係:<br />\nA1 A2 A3 A4 A6 A7 <br />\nB1 B6 B8 B11<br />\n每人限買三杯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原因係想多d人飲到 希望大家諒解<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而捐款亦都係會比立場 因為有報導出左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有人提意捐 傳真社 / 獨媒 <br />\n我地下一次就決定到佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後希望大家唔好忘記呢五個月黎發生既事！<br />\n我地會盡最大努力支持你地！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不割席！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"c32bd5b8a27eb39bff3db29376278bb809be97d1","tid":1697932,"uid":123926,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:26:30.000Z","msg":"你嘅好意我地心領喇, <br />\n錢我地又唔係無,<br />\n不如將當日嘅錢捐出黎俾有需要嘅手足啦"},{"pid":"ae6b3d682ae4e1f08b09008ae65e0616f1f3f9ee","tid":1697932,"uid":247719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:31:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b8b0353d365001e51928a8dcf86a02a5ccb413a","tid":1697932,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:34:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bvCTcoV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbvCTcoV.jpg&h=87c59ce4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0JWXE34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0JWXE34.jpg&h=9d8ce577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o7rQfCq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo7rQfCq.jpg&h=dfa0a304&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[重新整合]11.10 7區開花！ 11.11全港3罷！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697199\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697199</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n樽頸突破！11 11 黎明行動 7:00 18區集合 行動強制罷工！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1696996\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1696996</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2da904c1b689ea8d90ed3a3cd2500cbf804ad33e","tid":1697932,"uid":225169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:34:36.000Z","msg":"可以可以放款C都指定飲品到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9e73b04e4d4642bb5792de2dcb09fe561ea741","tid":1697932,"uid":4360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:24:47.000Z","msg":"b11係咪tea dragon<br />\n係嘅我all in<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3af011428acbdcaa14a08bd0b8815d66bf5ffa4","tid":1697932,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:31:31.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"ab7f282353abaef23b4ae4f8a8bf9333f75d78c2","tid":1697932,"uid":310775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:56:41.000Z","msg":"你咁樣我哋會唔捨得嗌口號㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae0aea8e98d01072ff994cfeddf4a7b0bdcd0c8","tid":1697932,"uid":211347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:00:41.000Z","msg":"如果派哂有冇得照買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031b3f3b35a4aa61be7d622fe9c9d528f7a8201e","tid":1697932,"uid":304230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c32bd5b8a27eb39bff3db29376278bb809be97d1","tid":1697932,"uid":123926,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:26:30.000Z","msg":"你嘅好意我地心領喇, <br />\n錢我地又唔係無,<br />\n不如將當日